<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 21 at 9:57AM MDT  by NWS El Paso</headline>
<description>BURSTS OF HEAVY SNOW ON SAN AUGUSTIN PASS
At 9:50AM, webcams and observations are showing moderate to heavy
snow across San Augustin Pass along US-70. Expect a rapid
reduction in visibility and very slick road conditions. Moderate
to heavy snow will continue for at least the next hour with
hazardous travel conditions expected for motorists.</description>
